During 0-1 each task completes its first initiate

During 1-2 each task completes its second initiate

During 2-3
   Task 1 completes its request (i.e., the request is granted)
   Task 2's request cannot be granted

During 3-4
   First check blocked tasks:
       task 2's request cannot be granted
   Task 1 completes its request

During 4-5
   First check blocked tasks:
       task 2's request cannot be granted
   Task 1 releases

During 5-6
   First check blocked tasks:
       task 2's request cannot be granted
   Task 1 releases and terminates (at 6)

During 6-7
   First check blocked tasks:
      Task 2 completes its request

During 7-8
   Task 2 completes its request

During 8-9
   Task 2 releases

During 9-10
   Task 2 releases and terminates (at 10)
